OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773234702
OL,3,CDocklands bombing victim says he
OL,4,Cbelieves Gerry Adams played 'major
OL,5,Cpart' in IRA
OL,7,FA man injured in the Docklands bombing
OL,8,Fhas said he believes Gerry Adams
OL,9,Fplayed a "major part" in the IRA.
OL,11,FJonathan Ganesh, giving evidence at
OL,12,Fthe High Court in London in a civil
OL,13,Fcase brought against the former Sinn
OL,14,FFein president, told how his mental
OL,15,Fhealth had suffered as he "relived the
OL,16,Fnightmare" of the bombing.
OL,26,@qD@JOUqD@UO]wD@[OUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773234702
OL,3,CDocklands bombing victim says he
OL,4,Cbelieves Gerry Adams played 'major
OL,5,Cpart' in IRA
OL,7,FThe witness also denied a suggestion
OL,8,Fthat he had taken the case against Mr
OL,9,FAdams only because of the introduction
OL,10,Fof the previous government's Legacy
OL,11,FAct.
OL,13,FMr Ganesh was injured in the 1996
OL,14,FLondon Docklands bombing, which killed
OL,15,Fhis friends Inam Bashir and John
OL,16,FJeffries and injured more than 100
OL,17,Fothers.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773234702
OL,3,CDocklands bombing victim says he
OL,4,Cbelieves Gerry Adams played 'major
OL,5,Cpart' in IRA
OL,7,FAlong with John Clark, a victim of the
OL,8,F1973 Old Bailey bombing in London, and
OL,9,FBarry Laycock, a victim of the 1996
OL,10,FArndale shopping centre bombing in
OL,11,FManchester, the three men allege that
OL,12,FMr Adams was a leading member of the
OL,13,FProvisional IRA on those dates,
OL,14,Fincluding of its Army Council.
OL,16,FThey are seeking #1 in damages.
OL,18,FMr Adams denies that he had any role
OL,19,Fin the Provisional IRA and is opposing
OL,20,Fthe claim.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773234702
OL,3,CDocklands bombing victim says he
OL,4,Cbelieves Gerry Adams played 'major
OL,5,Cpart' in IRA
OL,7,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson attended
OL,8,Fcourt on Tuesday with his party MP
OL,9,FGregory Campbell.
OL,11,FOutside court, Mr Robinson said it
OL,12,Fwould be "seismic" if the court
OL,13,Fconcluded Mr Adams was an IRA member.
OL,15,F"We think that this is an important
OL,16,Fcase," he told reporters.
OL,18,F"If our system establishes that he
OL,19,Fwas, and that liability rests with
OL,20,Fhim, then that will be seismic.
OL,26,@tD@JOUtD@RO]wD@AOUxD@FO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773234702
OL,3,CDocklands bombing victim says he
OL,4,Cbelieves Gerry Adams played 'major
OL,5,Cpart' in IRA
OL,7,F"It is true that he was the leader of
OL,8,Fa republican movement that was
OL,9,Fresponsible for breaking hearts and
OL,10,Fhomes and scarring our nation, and
OL,11,Ftoday, in this case, is an opportunity
OL,12,Ffor justice for victims and that's why
OL,13,Fwe're here."
OL,15,FAnne Studd KC, representing the three
OL,16,Fmen, asked Mr Ganesh what was his
OL,17,Fcatalyst for bringing the proceedings.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773234702
OL,3,CDocklands bombing victim says he
OL,4,Cbelieves Gerry Adams played 'major
OL,5,Cpart' in IRA
OL,7,FMr Ganesh said he was "very concerned
OL,8,Fregarding Mr Adams' behaviour" in
OL,9,Fbringing legal action against the UK
OL,10,FGovernment.
OL,12,FHe said: "I felt that is not right for
OL,13,Fall of the innocent victims who have
OL,14,Fsuffered."
OL,16,FJames Robottom, representing Mr Adams,
OL,17,Fasked Mr Ganesh if he was bringing the
OL,18,Fclaim to seek justice.
OL,20,FHe said: "Some kind of justice, that
OL,21,Fis correct."
OL,26,@oD@WOUpD@^O]tD@JOUvD@JO]|D@JOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773234702
OL,3,CDocklands bombing victim says he
OL,4,Cbelieves Gerry Adams played 'major
OL,5,Cpart' in IRA
OL,7,FThe barrister asked if he was also
OL,8,Fbringing the case on behalf of other
OL,9,FIRA victims.
OL,11,FMr Ganesh said: "That would be a fair
OL,12,Fstatement."
OL,14,FMr Robottom said: "You want to be able
OL,15,Fto say Gerry Adams is the man
OL,16,Fresponsible for the bombing that
OL,17,Finjured you?"
OL,26,@sD@QOUtD@KO]vD@SOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773234702
OL,3,CDocklands bombing victim says he
OL,4,Cbelieves Gerry Adams played 'major
OL,5,Cpart' in IRA
OL,7,FMr Ganesh said: "I don't suggest for
OL,8,Fone minute that Mr Adams drove the
OL,9,Florry or planted the bomb but I do
OL,10,Fbelieve he played a major part in the
OL,11,FIRA and I thought he had some
OL,12,Finvolvement with the attack."
OL,14,FThe barrister said: "You believed in
OL,15,Fthe aftermath of the bombing that your
OL,16,Finjuries were attributable, caused by
OL,17,FGerry Adams?"
OL,19,FThe witness said: "I believe he had
OL,20,Fsome involvement in it but I don't
OL,21,Fbelieve he actually planted the bomb."
OL,26,@oD@QOUtD@]O]vD@UOUyD@MO]{D@SOU}D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773234702
OL,3,CDocklands bombing victim says he
OL,4,Cbelieves Gerry Adams played 'major
OL,5,Cpart' in IRA
OL,7,FThe barrister questioned the witness
OL,8,Fabout why he did not bring the case
OL,9,Fagainst Mr Adams years earlier.
OL,11,FMr Ganesh said after the 1996 bombing
OL,12,Fhe was angry, but never opposed the
OL,13,Fpeace process in Northern Ireland,
OL,14,Feven though it led to the early
OL,15,Frelease from prison of James McArdle,
OL,16,Fwho had been convicted of the
OL,17,FDocklands attack.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773234702
OL,3,CDocklands bombing victim says he
OL,4,Cbelieves Gerry Adams played 'major
OL,5,Cpart' in IRA
OL,7,FHe said he thought the Good Friday
OL,8,FAgreement in 1998 would have prevented
OL,9,Fhim from bringing a compensation claim
OL,10,Fagainst Mr Adams earlier.
OL,12,FHe said: "In my heart I was hoping the
OL,13,Fpeace process would work."
OL,15,FMr Ganesh said it was only when Mr
OL,16,FAdams announced his intention to sue
OL,17,Fthe Government, that he explored the
OL,18,Fpossibility of bringing a case against
OL,19,Fhim.
OL,26,@tD@JOUuD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773234702
OL,3,CDocklands bombing victim says he
OL,4,Cbelieves Gerry Adams played 'major
OL,5,Cpart' in IRA
OL,7,FMr Ganesh said he had previously been
OL,8,Fawarded #1,000 by the criminal
OL,9,Finjuries compensation scheme due to
OL,10,Fshrapnel injuries.
OL,12,FHe told the court he was later
OL,13,Fdiagnosed with post-traumatic stress
OL,14,Fdisorder and had received extensive
OL,15,Ftreatment.
OL,17,FThe barrister asked if he had
OL,18,Fconsidered making another claim for
OL,19,Fcompensation, based on his mental
OL,20,Fhealth issues.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773234702
OL,3,CDocklands bombing victim says he
OL,4,Cbelieves Gerry Adams played 'major
OL,5,Cpart' in IRA
OL,7,FMr Ganesh told the court: "My primary
OL,8,Fconcern was to get myself well... that
OL,9,Fwas my primary goal, not to seek
OL,10,Fcompensation.
OL,12,F"When you are in a very dark place,
OL,13,Fyou keep reliving that nightmare all
OL,14,Fthe time, you relive it like a record
OL,15,Fthat keeps playing all the time.
OL,17,F"The last thing I was thinking about
OL,18,Fwas receiving substantial
OL,19,Fcompensation. I just wanted to get my
OL,20,Fhealth better."
OL,26,@oD@[OUtD@AOUyD@AOU|D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773234702
OL,3,CDocklands bombing victim says he
OL,4,Cbelieves Gerry Adams played 'major
OL,5,Cpart' in IRA
OL,7,FMr Robottom asked Mr Ganesh about his
OL,8,Fefforts, through work with the
OL,9,FDocklands Victims Association (DVA),
OL,10,Fto get compensation for victims for
OL,11,FLibyan involvement in the 1996 attack.
OL,13,FMr Ganesh said he had not mentioned
OL,14,Fthe DVA in his statement to the court
OL,15,Fas he did not believe it was relevant
OL,16,Fto the current case against Mr Adams.
OL,18,FMr Robottom asked Mr Ganesh if the
OL,19,F"real reason" he had brought the civil
OL,20,Fcase because of the introduction of
OL,21,Fthe previous government's Legacy Act.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773234702
OL,3,CDocklands bombing victim says he
OL,4,Cbelieves Gerry Adams played 'major
OL,5,Cpart' in IRA
OL,7,FHe asked: "This claim could have been
OL,8,Fbrought by you at any stage in the
OL,9,Flast 25 to 28 years, do you accept
OL,10,Fthat?"
OL,12,FMr Ganesh responded: "I think if you
OL,13,Fhad seen me 25 years ago I think even
OL,14,Fyou would concur with me I was (in) no
OL,15,Fcondition even (to) hold down a job or
OL,16,Feven feed myself properly."
OL,26,@oD@KOUrD@FO]tD@VOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773234702
OL,3,CDocklands bombing victim says he
OL,4,Cbelieves Gerry Adams played 'major
OL,5,Cpart' in IRA
OL,7,FThe barrister said: "Over 25 years Mr
OL,8,FAdams wasn't the chief person or
OL,9,Fanywhere near the chief person you
OL,10,Fwere seeking vindication for what you
OL,11,Fhave been through from.
OL,13,F"He wasn't that important. Libya was
OL,14,Fimportant, seeking justice through the
OL,15,FDVA was important. The only reason
OL,16,Fthis claim was brought in 2022 was
OL,17,Fbecause the Legacy Act was coming in
OL,18,Fand you were seeking justice against
OL,19,Fthe first person you could find."
OL,26,@oD@UOUuD@AOU{D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773234702
OL,3,CDocklands bombing victim says he
OL,4,Cbelieves Gerry Adams played 'major
OL,5,Cpart' in IRA
OL,7,FMr Ganesh said: "That is not true at
OL,8,Fall."
OL,10,FBefore lunch, the trial heard from Mr
OL,11,FLaycock.
OL,13,FMr Robottom asked him why he was
OL,14,Fbringing the case decades after the
OL,15,FArndale bombing.
OL,17,FMr Laycock said he had decided that if
OL,18,FMr Adams was bringing a legal case
OL,19,Fagainst the Government, he wanted to
OL,20,Fbring a case against the former Sinn
OL,21,FFein leader.
OL,26,@oD@QOUpD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
