CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773234702
OL,3,CDocklands bombing victim says he
OL,4,Cbelieves Gerry Adams played 'major
OL,5,Cpart' in IRA
OL,7,FThe witness said he wanted the "truth
OL,8,Fto be established" during the hearing.
OL,10,FHe added: "I think he (Mr Adams) had
OL,11,Fan involvement with the IRA."
OL,13,FMr Adams was in the courtroom in
OL,14,FLondon as the evidence was delivered.
OL,16,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson and party MP
OL,17,FGregory Campbell were also in the
OL,18,Fcourtroom on Tuesday.
OL,20,FThe trial before Mr Justice Swift is
OL,21,Fexpected to end next week.
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@RO]rD@KOUsD@]O]
